val costs", "bbox": [113.3, 1112.4, 386.4, 1131.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [762.3, 1112.4, 772.7, 1131.2]}, {"text": "2,044", "bbox": [788.3, 1112.4, 834.1, 1131.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [874.8, 1112.4, 885.3, 1131.2]}, {"text": "2,033", "bbox": [900.8, 1112.4, 946.7, 1131.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [978.0, 1112.4, 988.5, 1131.2]}, {"text": "2,044", "bbox": [1004.0, 1112.4, 1049.9, 1131.2]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1090.6, 1112.4, 1101.0, 1131.2]}, {"text": "2,033", "bbox": [1116.6, 1112.4, 1162.4, 1131.2]}, {"text": "Asset retirement obligation regulatory expense difference", "bbox": [113.3, 1134.1, 612.2, 1152.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [762.1, 1134.1, 772.5, 1152.8]}, {"text": "868", "bbox": [803.2, 1134.1, 834.0, 1152.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [874.7, 1134.1, 885.1, 1152.8]}, {"text": "786", "bbox": [915.8, 1134.1, 946.5, 1152.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [977.9, 1134.1, 988.3, 1152.8]}, {"text": "868", "bbox": [1019.0, 1134.1, 1049.7, 1152.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1090.4, 1134.1, 1100.8, 1152.8]}, {"text": "786", "bbox": [1131.5, 1134.1, 1162.2, 1152.8]}, {"text": "Pension", "bbox": [113.3, 1155.7, 219.6, 1174.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [762.3, 1155.7, 772.7, 1174.4]}, {"text": "531", "bbox": [803.4, 1155.7, 834.3, 1174.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [875.0, 1155.7, 885.4, 1174.4]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [940.5, 1155.7, 946.7, 1174.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [978.1, 1155.7, 988.5, 1174.4]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1043.6, 1155.7, 1049.8, 1174.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1090.6, 1155.7, 1101.0, 1174.4]}, {"text": "-", "bbox": [1156.1, 1155.7, 1162.3, 1174.4]}, {"text": "Other", "bbox": [113.3, 1177.3, 199.2, 1196.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [762.1, 1177.3, 772.5, 1196.0]}, {"text": "209", "bbox": [803.2, 1177.3, 833.9, 1196.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [874.6, 1177.3, 885.0, 1196.0]}, {"text": "256", "bbox": [915.7, 1177.3, 946.5, 1196.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [977.8, 1177.3, 988.2, 1196.0]}, {"text": "209", "bbox": [1018.9, 1177.3, 1049.7, 1196.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1090.4, 1177.3, 1100.8, 1196.0]}, {"text": "256", "bbox": [1131.5, 1177.3, 1162.2, 1196.0]}, {"text": "See Note 1 for a discussion of FPL Group's and FPL's other significant accounting policies.", "bbox": [112.5, 1220.5, 865.8, 1239.3]}, {"text": "Energy Marketing and Trading and Market Risk Sensitivity", "bbox": [112.5, 1264.6, 688.1, 1285.5]}, {"text": "Energy Marketing and Trading – Certain of FPL Group's subsidiaries, including FPL and FPL Energy, use derivative", "bbox": [112.5, 1309.9, 1162.4, 1328.6]}, {"text": "instruments (primarily swaps, options and forwards) to manage the commodity price risk inherent in the purchase and sale of", "bbox": [112.5, 1331.5, 1162.5, 1350.3]}, {"text": "fuel and electricity, as well as to optimize the value of power generation assets.  FPL Energy provides full energy and capacity", "bbox": [112.5, 1353.1, 1162.9, 1371.9]}, {"text": "requirements services to distribution utilities in certain markets and engages in energy trading activities to take advantage of", "bbox": [112.5, 1374.8, 1162.7, 1393.5]}, {"text": "expected future favorable price movements.", "bbox": [112.5, 1396.4, 466.2, 1415.1]}, {"text": "Derivative instruments, when required to be marked to market under FAS 133, as amended, are recorded on FPL Group's and", "bbox": [112.5, 1439.6, 1162.4, 1458.4]}, {"text": "FPL's consolidated balance sheets as either an asset or liability measured at fair value.  At FPL, substantially all changes in", "bbox": [112.5, 1461.2, 1162.5, 1480.0]}, {"text": "fair value are deferred as a regulatory asset or liability until the contracts are settled.  Upon settlement, any gains or losses are", "bbox": [112.5, 1482.9, 1162.6, 1501.6]}, {"text": "passed through the fuel clause or the capacity clause.  For FPL Group's non-rate regulated operations, predominantly FPL", "bbox": [112.5, 1504.5, 1162.4, 1523.2]}, {"text": "Energy, essentially all changes in the derivatives' fair value for power purchases and sales and trading activities are", "bbox": [112.5, 1526.1, 1162.4, 1544.9]}, {"text": "recognized on a net basis in operating revenues; fuel purchases and sales are recognized net in fuel, purchased power and", "bbox": [112.5, 1547.7, 1162.6, 1566.5]}]}